description:
On this week’s mini-episode, Kate and Doree hear from a caller with liberating wedding advice, share listener feedback about embracing curly hair, and discuss cultivating and practicing empathy.


To leave a voicemail for a future mini-ep, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.
